I raised this on discourse but did not get a feedback. Thought I would raise it here. Maybe I am doing something wrong? (Fyi I am on windows)

Code:
```julia
fib(n::Int)::Int = begin
    if n == 0 || n == 1
        return n
    elseif n == 2 
        return 1
    else
        return fib(n - 1) + fib(n - 2)
    end
end
```

In Julia 1.9
`@btime fib(40) # 380.588ms`

In Master commit f407a4cac3
`@btime fib(40) # 1.034s`

